590
00:25:23,880 --> 00:25:25,360
However...

591
00:25:25,440 --> 00:25:26,560
I can see Madame.

592
00:25:26,640 --> 00:25:27,520
What?

593
00:25:28,160 --> 00:25:30,520
It's a shame the bottom has a crack.

594
00:25:31,080 --> 00:25:33,760
Next, it's Hotta's beer mug.

595
00:25:33,840 --> 00:25:34,720
I'm so nervous.

596
00:25:34,800 --> 00:25:36,760
I didn't expect myself
to get so nervous.

597
00:25:36,840 --> 00:25:39,840
So, is it fired nicely?

598
00:25:39,920 --> 00:25:42,040
Wow, amazing!

599
00:25:42,120 --> 00:25:44,720
Thank you!

600
00:25:44,800 --> 00:25:46,200
What?

601
00:25:46,280 --> 00:25:47,760
