to celebrate Madame's 80th birthday.

644
00:27:30,120 --> 00:27:31,280
- Amazing.
- So cute.

645
00:27:31,360 --> 00:27:34,440
- Happy 80th birthday.
- Happy birthday.

646
00:27:34,520 --> 00:27:37,360
But you all made so much effort
to make them,

647
00:27:37,440 --> 00:27:39,240
so take those you like

648
00:27:39,320 --> 00:27:40,720
