you don't want.

649
00:27:40,800 --> 00:27:42,800
How kind of you.

650
00:27:42,880 --> 00:27:44,520
We'll give
what we want to give Madame.

651
00:27:44,600 --> 00:27:45,480
- Yes.
- Yes.

652
00:27:45,560 --> 00:27:47,560
I'll give this to Mr Degawa.

653
00:27:49,120 --> 00:27:50,840
Shigaraki ware...

654
00:27:50,920 --> 00:27:53,320
A great success!

655
00:27:53,400 --> 00:27:57,120
- Madame, happy 80th birthday!
- Thank you.

656
00:27:57,200 --> 00:27:59,400
Thank you. Thank you.

657
00:27:59,480 --> 00:28:02,960
That concludes Dewi Girls' Party,
Shigaraki Ware.

658
00:28:03,040 --> 00:28:04,760
- Interesting.
