668
00:28:27,280 --> 00:28:28,360
Yes.

669
00:28:28,440 --> 00:28:29,920
Why did we have to do that?

670
00:28:30,000 --> 00:28:32,200
It took us a whole day.

671
00:28:32,280 --> 00:28:34,360
It took us one whole day.

672
00:28:34,440 --> 00:28:36,280
- What do you think, Imoto?
- Well...

673
00:28:36,360 --> 00:28:39,440
I thought pottery is only using
the potter's wheel,

674
00:28:39,520 --> 00:28:40,920
but after watching this,

675
00:28:41,000 --> 00:28:43,200
the whole process
of making it from soil,

676
00:28:43,280 --> 00:28:45,280
I now know it's very difficult.

677
00:28:45,360 --> 00:28:49,360
