00:31:03,440 --> 00:31:05,040
First, it's Dewa Sanzan.

731
00:31:05,120 --> 00:31:06,200
Dewa Sanzan.

732
00:31:06,280 --> 00:31:09,000
It literally refers to
the three mountains

733
00:31:09,080 --> 00:31:11,240
in north Yamagata.

734
00:31:11,320 --> 00:31:13,320
It hasn't been shown in the media,

735
00:31:13,400 --> 00:31:15,920
but the shrine
has amazing spiritual energy.

736
00:31:16,000 --> 00:31:18,840
When we tried
and asked for permission,

737
00:31:18,920 --> 00:31:22,800
we were told that we could film
if we go to visit formally.

738
00:31:23,480 --> 00:31:26,800
This is the formal wear,
mountain priest style.

739
00:31:26,880 --> 00:31:32,360
