1036
00:44:19,320 --> 00:44:20,600
Turn, tap.

1037
00:44:21,280 --> 00:44:25,360
Hit the knees nine times.

1038
00:44:25,440 --> 00:44:28,600
Hit the knees nine times.

1039
00:44:29,480 --> 00:44:32,280
Now, they'll show us
the result of their practice.

1040
00:44:49,440 --> 00:44:51,440
Yoshiko, well done.

1041
00:44:53,080 --> 00:44:54,480
The two in front are good.

1042
00:44:54,560 --> 00:44:55,720
Choi, choi!

1043
00:44:56,120 --> 00:45:00,000
"Yonezawa beef hamburger,
Yonezawa steak, and Bistro Hikousen"

1044
00:45:00,080 --> 00:45:03,520
They were treated kindly
everywhere they went.

1045
00:45:03,600 --> 00:45:06,080
Thank you, people of Yamagata.

1046
00:45:06,160 --> 00:45:08,440
You went to Ginzan Onsen?
Isn't it fantastic?

1047
00:45:08,520 --> 00:45:09,400
It's amazing.

1048
00:45:09,480 --> 00:45:10,680
It's Haikara-San:
Here Comes Miss Modern.

1049
00:45:10,760 --> 00:45:12,800
Haikara-San...

1050
00:45:12,880 --> 00:45:14,280
She looks so fat.

1051
00:45:14,360 --> 00:45:15,960
She's really fat.

1052
00:45:16,040 --> 00:45:17,720
How rich is her family?

1053
00:45:17,800 --> 00:45:20,120
How spoilt is this girl?

1054
00:45:20,200 --> 00:45:22,440
Her parents would say she's lovely.

1055
00:45:24,880 --> 00:45:27,880
That concludes their trip
to Yamagata.

1056
00:45:27,960 --> 00:45:29,160
How was it, Oshima?

1057
00:45:29,240 --> 00:45:31,320
They had a lot of fun.

1058
00:45:31,400 --> 00:45:35,280
We've been doing scary things
in The Quest so far,

1059
00:45:35,360 --> 00:45:39,760
so I would root for them,
but I was totally relaxed today.

1060
00:45:39,840 --> 00:45:41,840
You see,
Yakko didn't call it "filming".

1061
00:45:41,920 --> 00:45:44,520
She kept saying it was a trip.

1062
00:45:44,600 --> 00:45:47,800
The three of you seemed to have
enjoyed yourselves a lot,

1063
00:45:47,880 --> 00:45:53,600
but after I saw the twitching
of Yoshiko's left eye, it was...

1064
00:45:53,680 --> 00:45:55,280
- It must've been tough.
- Yes.

1065
00:45:55,360 --> 00:45:59,080
It twitched most often
in the bullet train journey back.

1066
00:46:00,480 --> 00:46:02,800
It kept twitching.

